        <p>Postgraduates at &nbsp;ONMU are taught in English, Ukrainian and Russian languages according to the programs and curriculum approved by the Ministry of Health of Ukraine. We take into consideration the peculiarities of public health services of the state where trainees come from.</p>
        <p>At&nbsp;<strong>Odessa National Medical University “ODNMU”,&nbsp;</strong>the following countries citizens are studying at the time: USA, Canada, Mexico, Ecuador, Peru, Brazil, Chili, Australia, UK, Germany, Spain, Portugal, France, Norway, Denmark, Sweden, Bulgaria, Moldova, Russia, Uzbekistan, Turkmenistan, Kazakhstan, Tajikistan, India, Pakistan, Sri Lanka, Maldives, Mauritius, Bangladesh, Nepal, Iran, Iraq, Morocco, Tunis, Saudi Arabia, United Arab Emirates, Bahrain, Yemen, Israel, Palestine, Kuwait, Oman, Lebanon, Egypt, Libya, Algeria, Malaysia, Nigeria, Ghana, Benin, Togo, South Africa, Zambia, Zimbabwe, Botswana, Namibia, Angola, Kenya, Tanzania, Cameroon, Uganda, Lesotho, China, etc.</p>
